## Images

![[diagram.png]]

![[photo.png|240]]

![alt text](./local.png)

![remote](https://example.com/pic.png)

An inline ![x](y.png) image stays a paragraph.

 ---

(heading H2 @0..10
  "Images")
(image Embed("diagram.png") "diagram.png" @11..28)
(image Embed("photo.png") "photo.png" @29..48)
(image Path("./local.png") "alt text" @49..74)
(image Url("https://example.com/pic.png") "remote" @75..114)
(paragraph @115..162
  "An inline "
  "x"
  " image stays a paragraph.")
